32#include "gmp.h"
33#include "gmp-impl.h"
34
35void
36mpz_fdiv_q (mpz_ptr quot, mpz_srcptr dividend, mpz_srcptr divisor)
37{
38 mp_size_t dividend_size = SIZ (dividend);
39 mp_size_t divisor_size = SIZ (divisor);
40 mpz_t rem;
41 TMP_DECL;
42
43 TMP_MARK;
44
45 MPZ_TMP_INIT (rem, ABS (divisor_size));
46
47 mpz_tdiv_qr (quot, rem, dividend, divisor);
48
49 if ((divisor_size ^ dividend_size) < 0 && SIZ (rem) != 0)
50 mpz_sub_ui (quot, quot, 1L);
51
52 TMP_FREE;
53}
